components.name: EniRadioComponent
components.templateData:
<fieldset
class="eni-group-radio-button"
role="radiogroup"
[attr.aria-labelledby]="name"
>
<input

  [name]="name"
  type="text"
  class="eni-radio-input"
  [required]="required"
  minLength="1"
    [(ngModel)]="value"

>
<legend [id]="name" class="eni-group-radio-button-label" >
 {{title}}
</legend>



    <button
    *ngFor="let element of radio; let index = index"
      role="radio"
      [disabled]="element.disabled"
      [class]="'eni-radio-button ' + valueIsDisabled(element) + ' ' + valueIsCheck(element)"

      [attr.aria-checked]="element.value === value ? true : false"
      (click)="valueSetter(element)"
    >
      {{element.value}}
    </button>

</fieldset>
